00:56.688 --> 01:00.752
Amberleigh is still with us
if we're pure enough to hear her.

01:00.752 --> 01:02.280
Why did you kill Amberleigh?

01:02.280 --> 01:04.328
She died...

01:04.328 --> 01:06.829
