01:07.249 --> 01:09.539
In a moment of intense love.

01:10.331 --> 01:11.226
Excuse us.

01:11.547 --> 01:12.557
Out of the way!

01:12.557 --> 01:14.475
Mr. Fife, tell us about your love.

01:14.475 --> 01:16.033
NYPD!

01:16.033 --> 01:18.813
Look, folks, move out of the way.
There's no more questions.

01:18.813 --> 01:19.829
Thank you, please.

01:19.829 --> 01:21.054
Did he kill her? Are you sure?

01:21.054 --> 01:22.601
Simon Henry Fife?

01:22.601 --> 01:25.253
NYPD. He's in our custody now.

01:25.253 --> 01:26.530
Simon, are you ready?

01:26.530 --> 01:28.793
- How are you feeling?
- Back off!

01:28.793 --> 01:30.775
Autumn in New York?

01:30.775 --> 01:32.144
It's time I go home.

01:32.144 --> 01:34.152
- All right.
- Excuse me, stand back.

01:37.018 --> 01:38.527
